  "body": " I've asked for help in the [Truffle Gitter](http://gitter.im/Consensys/truffle) before filing this issue.\r\n\r\n---------------------------\r\n\r\n## Issue\r\ndeep file dependency issue.\r\n\r\n> execSync@1.0.2 install /root/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/truffle/node_modules/execSync\r\n> node install.js\r\n\r\nmodule.js:472\r\n    throw err;\r\n    ^\r\n\r\nError: Cannot find module '/root/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/truffle/node_modules/execSync/install.js'\r\n    at Function.Module._resolveFilename (module.js:470:15)\r\n    at Function.Module._load (module.js:418:25)\r\n    at Module.runMain (module.js:605:10)\r\n    at run (bootstrap_node.js:427:7)\r\n    at startup (bootstrap_node.js:151:9)\r\n    at bootstrap_node.js:542:3\r\n[               ...] / install: info lifecycle execSync@1.0.2~install: Failed \r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\nsudo npm install -g truffle \r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n* Operating System: MS (Linux bash)\r\n* node version: 7.0.0\r\n* npm version: 4.2.0\r\n",
